name: PATRIOT
description: The men and women who serve this country are the bedrock of our democracy. In honor of Veterans Day, the $PATRIOT token was created. $PATRIOT honors them by supporting and donating to local veteran charities across our community. 100% of collected fees go directly to veterans and their families. Built by Patriots, for Patriots on @america_dot_fun Join the battalion and back those who served. CA: pA3VznTTnS22JERJ2okMK3hFebbw8dEpWph6UCf6USA
